# 🏥 Flexi4U – Smart Health & Wellness Platform

Flexi4U is a full-stack web application designed to provide **smart physiotherapy, appointment booking, and health management** with a modern UI and secure authentication system.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 🔐 Authentication System

* Email & Password Login
* User Registration with OTP Verification
* Forgot Password using OTP Reset 🔥
* Secure JWT-based authentication
* Role-based login (User / Doctor)

---

### 📅 Appointment System

* Book appointments with doctors
* Real-time slot validation (no double booking)
* Upcoming / Past / Cancelled filtering
* Reschedule & Cancel options

---

### 🧠 Smart UI/UX

* Glassmorphism design ✨
* Fully responsive (mobile + desktop)
* Animated OTP input (Instagram-style)
* Password show/hide 👁️
* Live validation (confirm password, errors)

---

### 📊 Dashboard

* User profile management
* Health data (BMI, conditions, etc.)
* Clean navigation system

---

### 📩 OTP System

* Email OTP for:

  * Signup verification
  * Password reset
* Resend OTP timer (30 sec)
* Auto-focus OTP input boxes

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Frontend

* React (Vite)
* TypeScript
* Tailwind CSS
* Wouter (routing)
* React Query

### Backend

* Node.js
* Express.js
* MongoDB + Mongoose
* JWT Authentication
* OTP Generator

---

